{"tid":1287730,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"粒聲唔出其實已經可以令到啲犬隻淆底","createTime":"2019-07-05T10:30:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T10:52:30.000Z","uid":116504,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1bb8a3a3c0c07c5aef6c84924b73e04836acee41","tid":1287730,"uid":116504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T10:30:40.000Z","msg":"話說頭先收工係灣仔搭地鐵<br />\n有兩隻汪汪冇喇喇行埋黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />汪汪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />汪汪汪汪汪<br />\n<br />\n聽唔明 不過做過下幾秒動物傳心師 我明佢想睇身分證 利申 正氣撚 成世仔未試過比人查身分證 第一次 唯一有可能令佢查係自己件黑衫<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我望住隻汪汪 慢慢轉個背囊去前面 慢慢拎張身分證出黎<br />\n我繼續望住隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隻狗：<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />第一次call台對面都係咁汪 好似唔得閒&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />第一下見到我望住佢&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最後頭耷耷比番張證我<br />\n<br />\n拎完張證 我企定定繼續睇汪汪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n隻睇證狗一路走行幾步就望番轉頭 我就企係到睇佢睇到佢走左為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />見佢隻汪汪淆曬底又吠唔出聲真係爽 另一隻？梳 唔講唔記得 當左佢透明<br />\n<br />\nP.S.全程都冇出聲<br />\nBtw係咪查身分證都要寫落簿 定係依加先係咁？<br />\n<br />\n大家唔洗硬碰硬 淨係睇證可以好似我咁 尊敬地注視佢地對眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢地又吹你唔漲"},{"pid":"0140d1d58ba7ac14c9acbb785ca7c903c833c87c","tid":1287730,"uid":258973,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T10:32:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/_1366450026586cec922ddbe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nm